lead_paragraph: Seven has been a magic number for Japan's Hideki Matsuyama in recent weeks and it was no different at the Hero World Challenge in the Bahamas in Saturday's third round.

headline.print_headline: Golf: Seven Is the Charm for Leader Matsuyama in the Bahamas
